body: Man this is such a ridiculous piece of work. Nicely drawn with details where it matters but the entire french kissing (even with a bloody turtle for fucks sake) and the "let's cum together" nonsense,.... good grief. I mean, is this a hardcore bestiality hentai or a lovey dovey romance erotic manga?! If you (ab)use the animals for your own sexual desire, telling even that they only follow their instincts, don't try to twist it around at the end of each chapter and portray it as if they are in love with you. (눈_눈)
the way her friend just tossed her aside at first kinda ruined the first third for me
